[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0242","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0242.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0107","title":"Apache HTTP Server 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Apache 1.2.5 及更早版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送大量包含大量 `/` 字符的恶意 GET 请求触发此漏洞，导致 Apache 服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Apache 1.2.5 及之前所有版本，攻击无需身份认证，利用难度较低，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0107"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-12-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.150","remediation":"建议升级至 Apache 1.3.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复超大 GET 请求导致的缓冲区溢出。如无法升级，可在反向代理层（如 Nginx）限制单个 URI 长度不超过 4096 字节，并在 Web 应用防火墙中配置请求速率限制以缓解 DDoS 风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0107","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20558","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0107.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0107.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0107","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0107.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0107.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0107.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qq9g-rvjp-rm4j/GHSA-qq9g-rvjp-rm4j.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0107.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0242.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0241","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0241.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0106","title":"多种厂商 Finger 服务手指炸弹漏洞","description":"Finger 服务存在重定向功能滥用漏洞，远程攻击者可利用多个支持 Finger 协议的主机构建重定向链（finger bomb），迫使目标系统反复进行网络连接，造成流量放大或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响早期运行 Finger 服务的 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。建议禁用 Finger 服务或通过防火墙限制入站访问。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0106"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.040","remediation":"立即禁用 finger 服务（如 in.fingerd），在 inetd/xinetd 配置中注释掉 finger 行并重启服务。在防火墙上阻止外部对 TCP 端口 79 的访问。如确需使用，通过 tcp_wrappers（/etc/hosts.deny）限制仅允许可信来源 IP。建议升级到支持 finger 访问控制的实现或直接停用该协议。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0106"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0241.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0240","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0240.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0683","title":"Network Associates Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 ICMP Packet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Network Associates Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 在处理异常格式的 ICMP 数据包时存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标防火墙发送特制的畸形 ICMP 报文，触发异常的报文处理流程，导致防火墙服务崩溃或停止响应，从而阻断正常网络流量通过。该漏洞直接影响 Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0683"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.410","remediation":"Network Associates Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 已停止技术支持，官方不再发布安全补丁。建议立即升级至仍在支持周期内的现代防火墙产品。如需临时缓解，可在网络边界 ACL 中配置丢弃畸形 ICMP 报文（如分片 ICMP、长度异常 ICMP 等），并限制 ICMP 速率，减少拒绝服务攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1029","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/556","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19441","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0683.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0683","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0683.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0683.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3834-9q92-mj44/GHSA-3834-9q92-mj44.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0683.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e2ff807e9fd18d30d388cc2c559c111ff993a143/1999.tsv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0683.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0240.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0240.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0240.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0239","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0239.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0682","title":"Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 SMTP 邮件中继安全绕过漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange 5.5 存在电子邮件中继绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可以利用封装的 SMTP 地址格式（如\"<user@domain.com>\"嵌入在邮件地址字段中）发送邮件，即使服务器已启用防中继功能，仍能绕过限制将邮件中继到外部域。该漏洞可被垃圾邮件发送者利用来发送大量垃圾邮件，导致服务器被滥用为开放中继。影响 Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 版本，攻击无需认证，仅需构造特制邮件地址即可触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0682"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.280","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-027 提供的 Exchange Server 5.5 安全更新，该补丁使封装的 SMTP 地址同样受反中继保护。若无法安装补丁，可在 Internet Mail Service 属性中将中继权限限制为仅允许经过身份验证的用户，并禁用不必要的站点到站点 SMTP 中继功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ237927","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-056.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/567","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-027"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0239.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0236","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0236.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0103","title":"多厂商 UDP Echo/Chargen 服务数据包风暴拒绝服务漏洞","description":"UDP炸弹或UDP数据包风暴漏洞（UDP bomb/UDP packet storm）是指攻击者利用 UDP echo（回显）和 chargen（字符生成）等服务的组合特性，向目标服务器发送伪造源地址的数据包，使服务之间形成无限循环的数据包风暴，从而导致目标系统网络带宽耗尽、服务不可用。该漏洞影响早期 UNIX/Linux 系统中默认启用的 UDP 服务，属于拒绝服务类漏洞。攻击者无需认证即可远程发起攻击，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。该漏洞自 1999 年被发现至今仍可在未正确配置 UDP 服务的系统中利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0103"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-02-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:35.610","remediation":"禁用不必要的 UDP 服务（如 echo、chargen、time 等），在 /etc/inetd.conf 或 systemd socket 配置中注释或删除对应行并重启服务。在边界防火墙/路由器上阻止外部对 UDP 端口 7 (echo)、19 (chargen) 的访问，并限制内部 UDP 广播流量以防止放大攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://ics-cert.us-cert.gov/advisories/ICSMA-18-233-01","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/80171"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0236.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0235","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0235.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0102","title":"SLmail 3.x 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"SLmail 3.x 邮件服务器在处理邮件头 FROM 字段时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送含有超长 FROM 行的特制邮件触发该漏洞，导致内存越界写入，从而实现以邮件服务进程权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 SLmail 3.x 全系列版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0102"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-07-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:35.467","remediation":"立即升级 SLMail 至 3.2.0.3 以上版本，该版本修复了 FROM 行缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，应在边界防火墙上限制仅允许可信 IP 访问 SMTP 端口（25/tcp），并考虑迁移至长期维护的邮件服务器软件（如 Postfix 或 Exchange）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0102"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0235.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0234","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0234.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0681","title":"Microsoft FrontPage Personal Web Server 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft FrontPage Personal Web Server (PWS) 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送超长 URL 请求触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 95 平台上的 FrontPage Server Extensions 3.0.2.926 及可能其他版本，攻击无需身份认证，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0681"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.150","remediation":"立即停止使用 Windows 95 及 Microsoft FrontPage Personal Web Server 1.0，该产品已终止支持且不再有安全更新。建议迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 IIS 或 Apache），并在防火墙层面限制对 PWS 服务的网络访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/1999-q3/0381.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/568","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3117","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19445","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0681.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0681","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0681.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0681.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wj24-pvf2-wxpm/GHSA-wj24-pvf2-wxpm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_150600_150700.json","https://github.com/CERTCC/SBOM/blob/ae581e32992458f65018df4eced684b7370bba39/SwiftBOM/cpe_lookup/cve_lookup/microsoft/personal_web_server_cve.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0681.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0234.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0234.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0234.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0233","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0233.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0680","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Terminal Server 认证前资源消耗拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Terminal Server 在处理客户端新建连接请求时，在完成身份认证前会执行额外的资源分配操作，远程攻击者可通过发送大量未认证的连接请求消耗服务器资源，导致终端服务响应缓慢或完全停止响应，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 Terminal Server 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0680"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.027","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-028（KB Q238600）提供的补丁。Windows NT 4.0 Terminal Server 已停止技术支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上限制对 TCP 3389 端口的访问，仅允许受信任 IP 连接，并启用终端服务连接认证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ238600","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-057.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/571","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-028","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0680.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0680","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0680.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0680.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-65vm-7q8v-3p23/GHSA-65vm-7q8v-3p23.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0680.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000723.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0233.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0232","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0232.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0101","title":"IBM AIX/Microsoft Windows/Sun SunOS gethostbyname() 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 3.x/4.x、Windows 95/98/2000/NT 4.0 及 SunOS 5 等操作系统的 `gethostbyname()` 库函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送恶意的 DNS 主机名解析请求触发缓冲区溢出，导致任意代码执行，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响多个主流操作系统平台，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，对核心服务器和网络设备危害极大。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0101"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-12-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:35.340","remediation":"受影响系统均已停止安全技术支持，建议立即升级至厂商仍在支持的最新操作系统版本。AIX 用户应升级至 AIX 7.2 及以上；Solaris 用户升级至 Solaris 11.4；Windows 平台已无法通过官方补丁修复，须迁移至 Windows 10/11 或 Server 2016+。临时缓解措施：在网络边界防火墙或 DNS 服务器上过滤恶意 DNS 响应数据包，限制应用程序对 gethostbyname() 的输入长度。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/h-13.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/22251","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0101.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0101.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0101","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0101.json","https://github.com/doodad-labs/threat-intelligence/blob/ee308632cd35c3a8b60a89f181457ce4fae96eed/data/exploits/CVE-1999-0101.22251.sh","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0101.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/README.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2q9f-93v8-w2pf/GHSA-2q9f-93v8-w2pf.json","https://github.com/kylekirkby/Python-Exploit-Search-Tool/blob/8e84b77a6ff689ce32d04884f9ea75de04ae0433/platforms/multiple/remote/22251.sh","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0232.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0232.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0231","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0231.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0100","title":"IBM AIX innd 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 系统上的 INN（InterNetNews）新闻服务器 1.5.1 版本存在远程命令执行漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向 innd 守护进程发送特制的控制消息（control messages），利用其处理逻辑缺陷执行任意命令，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 平台的 INN 1.5.1，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0100"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:35.217","remediation":"升级 INN 至 2.0 及以上版本（当前最新为 2.7.x），旧版 innd 1.x 通过新闻组控制消息可远程执行命令，新版本已修复该问题。如无法升级，在 inn.conf 中将 `verify-cancel` 和 `verify-ihave` 设为 `always` 并限制 trusted peers 来源 IP 范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0100"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0231.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0229","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0229.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0098","title":"Sendmail SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sendmail SMTP 服务在处理 HELO 命令时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器的 25 端口发送特制的 HELO 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用可导致任意代码执行或服务崩溃，攻击者借此可完全控制服务器或隐藏恶意活动痕迹。该漏洞影响多个版本的 Sendmail，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0098"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.903","remediation":"立即升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.0 或更高版本（该版本修复了 SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出问题）。SLMail 用户应升级至 3.0 及以上版本，Mercury Mail Server 用户升级至最新版本。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙层面限制 SMTP（TCP 25）端口仅允许可信来源访问，同时在 Sendmail 配置中限制 HELO 命令输入长度作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0098"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0229.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0228","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0228.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0097","title":"IBM AIX FTP 客户端命令注入漏洞","description":"AIX FTP 客户端在处理来自恶意 FTP 服务器的响应时存在命令注入漏洞。攻击者通过在 FTP 协议响应中嵌入 shell 元字符（如管道符 |），当用户连接至攻击者控制的 FTP 服务器时，恶意内容被传递给 shell 执行，导致远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击者无需身份认证即可完全控制受害系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0097"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.750","remediation":"建议升级至 AIX 4.3.3 及以上维护版本，或安装 IBM APAR 安全补丁（IX72452 / IY07246）。如无法升级，可使用 OpenSSH sftp 替代 ftp 命令进行文件传输，或在 /usr/bin/ftp 上通过 chmod 移除不必要的执行权限以限制使用。避免使用 AIX ftp 客户端连接不可信或不受控的 FTP 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0097"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0228.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0225","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0225.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0679","title":"EFnet Hybrid IRCd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Hybrid IRCd 5.0.3 p7（及其衍生版本 hybrid-6）的 m_invite 命令处理函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 IRC 服务器发送特制的 INVITE 请求触发溢出，导致攻击者在服务器进程中执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 EFnet 等大型 IRC 网络中广泛部署的 hybrid 系列 IRC 服务器，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，利用代码已在 ExploitDB 公开。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0679"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:49.900","remediation":"升级到 hybrid-6 IRC 服务器高于 5.0.3 p7 的版本（如 b0、b1 或更高稳定版），该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可在 IRC 服务器配置中禁用 m_invite 命令，或通过防火墙限制对 IRC 端口（默认 6667）的访问来源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.efnet.org/archive/servers/hybrid/ChangeLog","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/581","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19459","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0679.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0679","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0679.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0679.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3c24-mx8q-qwqm/GHSA-3c24-mx8q-qwqm.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0679.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--53a24dd1-2f0b-4489-8912-d13ab5816b7a.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000727.txt","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0225.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0223","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0223.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0095","title":"Berkeley Sendmail Debug 命令远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Sendmail 5.58 及更早版本中默认启用了调试（debug）命令功能，远程攻击者可通过 SMTP 端口向目标发送特制的 debug 命令，以 root 权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 Berkeley Sendmail 邮件服务器，无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害等级严重。厂商已发布补丁禁用调试功能。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0095"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1988-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.460","remediation":"立即将 Sendmail 升级至 8.6.x 或更高版本，该系列已默认禁用 debug/wizard 调试命令。如无法升级，在 sendmail.cf 配置文件中添加 Ow 选项（即 O Wizard=no）以关闭 wiz 模式。在网络层面限制对 TCP 端口 25 的访问，仅允许可信来源连接 SMTP 服务作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://seclists.org/fulldisclosure/2019/Jun/16","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2019/06/05/4","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2019/06/06/1","http://www.osvdb.org/195","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19028","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0095.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0095.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0095","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/1999/CVE-1999-0095.rules","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0095.json","https://github.com/Mishthi27/SentrySense2.0/blob/de64bcf93503f6469484cdfdd5c26732e8f3f623/predictive_ai/threats/CVE-1999-0095.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0095.json","https://github.com/trailofbits/cb-multios/blob/810d7b24b1f62f56ef49b148fe155b0d0629cad2/challenges/REMATCH_1--Hat_Trick--Morris_Worm/README.md","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/663.txt","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0095.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0223.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0222","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0222.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0492","title":"GNU Ffingerd 远程用户名枚举漏洞","description":"` tags.<value>GNU Ffingerd 1.19 存在用户信息泄露漏洞，由于该服务在处理 finger 请求时未对响应进行统一处理，远程未经认证的攻击者可通过向目标系统发送包含特定用户名的 finger 查询请求，根据响应差异判断目标用户名是否存在。攻击者可利用此漏洞枚举系统有效用户，为后续暴力破解或针对性攻击提供信息支持。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0492"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.767","remediation":"升级 GNU Ffingerd 至 1.19 以上版本，或彻底禁用/卸载 finger 服务（如非业务必需）。如必须保留，可使用 tcp-wrappers（/etc/hosts.allow 和 /etc/hosts.deny）限制仅允许可信 IP 访问端口 79，并配置 xinetd 为仅允许特定来源连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0492","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20327"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0222.toml"}]